name: React-redux-starter-kit
tagline: Get started with React, Redux, React-Router and react-router-redux! (PC, Mobile and Admin)
body:
### Features
- [ANTD](http://ant.design/)

## Requirements

- node
- npm

## Getting Started

```
git clone https://github.com/xQuotes/react-redux-starter-kit.git
cd react-redux-starter-kit
npm install
npm run dev
```
